        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Cam-Follower Motion</text><text styleclass="Interface-Small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">: </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true">Since a</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Cam-Follower</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> is any </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Part</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> (but not a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Connecting Part</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">) in a kinematic-chain, the motion of a </text><text styleclass="Interface-Small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Cam-Follower</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> is very general. It may be:</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:9pt; color:#800000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2" translate="true">specified directly with a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2" translate="true">, and </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-FB-Motion-Dimension" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Motion-Dimension FB</link></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2" translate="true">from the measured motion of a different Part in a different kinematic-chain</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed2" translate="true">stationary</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
