        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Indexing:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> moves, then dwells, then moves forward again. An integer number of indexes complete one rotation.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Oscillating:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> swings back-and-forth.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Reciprocating</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: slides back-and-forth</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:normal;" translate="true">.</text></para>
